data.description: Gorgeous views of Lake Mendocino and Ukiah! This hilltop property is a 3 bedroom, 2 bath home, recently remodeled featuring a large, beautiful kitchen with stainless steel appliances and windows with views. Great room with high ceilings and picture window views from your dining room table, new flooring, new central heat and air, whole home generator and solar installed. Relax on the covered front porch and enjoy the sunrises and sunsets over the lake. 2 car garage and additional storage area. this 1.7 acre parcel is fully fenced with a gated entry. Cross fenced for animals. Don't miss this one!
